# Hey Ian LLC Website

Welcome to the repository for **Your IT Business Website**. This project is a responsive, one-page website template tailored for IT businesses. It includes a header, hero section, about section, services overview, and a contact form.

## Features

- **Responsive Design:** Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.
- **Clean Layout:** Modern and professional design with easy-to-navigate sections.
- **Customizable:** Simply modify the HTML and CSS to reflect your brandâ€™s identity.
- **GitHub Pages Ready:** Perfect for hosting on GitHub Pages with minimal setup.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- A web browser to preview the site.
- A text editor (e.g., Visual Studio Code) for making modifications.
- (Optional) Git to clone and manage the repository locally.

